RAWALPINDI, Sep 12 (APP): A soldier of Pakistan Army embraced martyrdom after an improvised explosive device (IED) exploded near security forces check post on Road Boya- Miranshah in Northwazirstan.
Sepoy Sajid, age 33 years embraced shahadat during the explosion, said an ISPR press release. The security forces had cordoned the area for clearance operation.
